NUMBER 2308
NAME Inside the Granite Tower, Red Room
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
CHANNEL 134
REGION 103
*DESCRIPTION_START
The stone walls of this room seem to be slightly melted causing the seams 
between the stones to run together. In the center of the room is a large 
boulder with some writing on it.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT S 2307
ITEM 0 367 ADJ1=178
EXTEND 0 with some writing on it.
IFPREVERB LOOK 0
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You notice that the boulder is melted and scorched as if from great heat. %cCarved into the front of the stone are the words:%c  "Flows like water,%c  fire of the earth.%c  It must be hotter,%c  to show its true worth."
ENDIF
IFPREVERB TOUCH 0
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER The boulder is warm to the touch.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB CAST 0
  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR SPELLNUM = 100
    ADD GFLAG1 3
    EQUAL SPELLNUM 999
  ENDIF
  IFVAR SPELLNUM = 117
    ADD GFLAG1 3
    EQUAL SPELLNUM 999
  ENDIF
  IFVAR SPELLNUM = 118
    ADD GFLAG1 2
    EQUAL SPELLNUM 999
  ENDIF
  IFVAR SPELLNUM = 112
    ADD GFLAG1 1
    EQUAL SPELLNUM 999
  ENDIF
  IFVAR SPELLNUM ! 999
    ECHO PLAYER You cast your spell at the boulder, but nothing happens.
    ECHO OTHERS %N cast at the boulder, but nothing happens.
    EQUAL SPELLNUM 0
    PLREVENT 1
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO ALL The air shimmers in one corner and a stone elemental appears.
    GENMON 131
  ENDIF
  IFVAR SPELLNUM = 999
    ECHO PLAYER Flame shoots from your hand and strikes the boulder.
    ECHO OTHERS Flames shoot from %N's hand and strikes the boulder.
    IFVAR FLAG1 < 11
      ECHO ALL The boulder shimmers with heat.
    ENDIF
    IFVAR FLAG1 < 21
      IFVAR FLAG1 > 10
        ECHO ALL The boulder begins to glow with intense heat.
      ENDIF
    ENDIF
    IFVAR FLAG1 < 30
      IFVAR FLAG1 > 20
        ECHO ALL The boulder shudders and begins to sag.
      ENDIF
    ENDIF
    IFVAR FLAG1 > 29
      ECHO ALL The boulder finally gives into your fiery attacks and melts into a puddle of cooling stone.
      ECHO ALL In the center of the cooling puddle you see a round crystal.
      REMOVEITEM 0
      NEWITEM 1 736
      NEWITEM 5 928 ADJ1=265
    ENDIF
ENDIF
