IFPREVERB PUSH 0
  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR FLAG2 = 1
    ECHO PLAYER You push against the boulder, but it doesn't budge.
    ECHO OTHERS You see %N push against the boulder, but nothing happens.
  ENDIF
  IFVAR FLAG1 = 0
    ECHO PLAYER You push against the boulder and it shifts back slightly.
    ECHO OTHERS You see %N push against the boulder, causing it to shift slightly.
    ADD GFLAG1 1
    EQUAL GFLAG2 1
  ENDIF
  IFVAR FLAG1 = 2
    ECHO PLAYER You push against the boulder and it seems to slip down the sword slightly.
    ECHO OTHERS You see %N push against the boulder causing it to slip down the sword slightly.
    ADD GFLAG1 1
    EQUAL GFLAG2 1
  ENDIF
  IFVAR FLAG1 = 4
    ECHO PLAYER You push on the boulder a final time causing it to crash to the ground and shatter revealing a triangular crystal.
    ECHO OTHERS You see %N push on the boulder a final time causing it to crash to the ground and shatter revealing a triangular crystal.
    REMOVEITEM 0
    NEWITEM 5 928 ADJ1=701
  ENDIF
ENDIF
