    ECHO PLAYER You pull on the boulder but nothing happens.
    ECHO OTHERS You see %N pull on the boulder but nothing happens.
  ENDIF
  IFVAR FLAG1 = 1
    ECHO PLAYER You pull on the boulder causing it to shift forward.
    ECHO OTHERS You see %N pull on the boulder causing it to shift forward.
    ADD GFLAG1 1
    EQUAL GFLAG2 0
  ENDIF
