    ECHO PLAYER You pull on the boulder causing it to wobble slightly.
    ECHO OTHERS You see %N pull on the boulder causing it to wobble slightly.
    ADD GFLAG1 1
    EQUAL GFLAG2 0
  ENDIF
ENDIF
